Imène El Ghazouani (Arabic: , amụrụ na 9 June 2000) bụ onye na-agba bọọlụ nke na-agba ọsọ dị ka onye na aga n'ihu maka Division 2 Féminine club GPSO 92 Issy
A mụrụ ya na France, ọ na anọchite anya Morocco na mba ụwa.
El Ghazouani agbaala bọọlụ maka La Rochette Vaux le Pénil FC, VGA Saint-Maur na Yzeure na France.
El Ghazouani mere nke mbụ ya na Morocco na 16 Septemba 2021 dị ka onye na anọchi anya nkeji 90+4 na mmeri 1-0 na Cameroon n'oge Aisha Buhari Cup.
